{"lemma":"ثَلاثَةٌ","slug":"ثَلاثَةٌ","root":"ثلث","root_slug":"ثلث","root_link":"/words/roots/ثلث","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ثَلاث","root":"ثلث","pos":"N","occurrence_count":8},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adv","num"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4629","n4630"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AB%D9%8E%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AB%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"num","gloss":"masculine of ثَلَاثَة (ṯalāṯa, “three”)","tags":["form-of","masculine"]},{"pos":"adv","gloss":"three at a time, in a group of three, in threes","examples":[{"text":"الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ فَاطِرِ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ جَاعِلِ الْمَلَائِكَةِ رُسُلًا أُولِي أَجْنِحَةٍ مَّثْنَىٰ وَثُلَاثَ وَرُبَاعَ ۚ يَزِيدُ فِي الْخَلْقِ مَا يَشَاءُ ۚ إِنَّ اللَّهَ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/θa.laːθ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4629","headword_ar":"ثَلَاثَةٌ","root":"vlv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", also written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"val`vapN","text_ar":"ثَلٰثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a noun of number, [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Three,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is masc., (S, M, Msb,) and is also written and pronounced ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulaAvapN","text_ar":"ثُلَاثَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm: (IAar, M, TA:) the fem. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"val`vN","text_ar":"ثَلٰثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Msb;) [and app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulaAvN","text_ar":"ثُلَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, mentioned above, under the head of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulaAvu","text_ar":"ثُلَاثُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but only as occurring with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw","text_ar":"ذُو"},{"kind":"text","text":"prefixed to it.] You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulaAvapu","text_ar":"ثُلَاثَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rijaAlK","text_ar":"رِجَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Three men"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nisowapK","text_ar":"نِسْوَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvu","text_ar":"ثَلَاثُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three women"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) In the saying of Mohammad, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rufiEa Alqalamu Eano valaAvK","text_ar":"رُفِعَ القَلَمُ عَنْ ثَلَاثٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The pen"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the recording angel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is withheld from three"},{"kind":"text","text":"persons]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlAv","text_ar":"ثلاث"},{"kind":"text","text":"is for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvi A^anofusK","text_ar":"ثَلَاثِ اَنْفُسٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb. [See art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rfE","text_ar":"رفع"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) [In like manner, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in several trads. for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvu","text_ar":"ثَلَاثُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSaAlK","text_ar":"خِصَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as, for instance, in the saying,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvN mano","text_ar":"ثَلَاثٌ مَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kun~a fiyhi HaAsabahu A@ll~`hu HisaAbFA yasiyrFA","text_ar":"كُنَّ فِيهِ حَاسَبَهُ ا@للّٰهُ حِسَابًا يَسِيرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[There are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three"},{"kind":"text","text":"qualities:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in whomsoever they be, God will reckon with him with an easy reckoning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: these are, thy giving to him who denies thee, and forgiving him who wrongs thee, and being kind to him who cuts thee off from him. (El-Jámi' es-Sagheer.) The people of El-Hijáz say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atawoniY valaAvatahumo","text_ar":"اَتَوْنِى ثَلَاثَتَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The three of them came to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arobaEatahumo","text_ar":"اَرْبَعَتَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and so on to ten [inclusive], with nasb in every case; and in like manner in the fem., ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayonaniY valaAvahun~a","text_ar":"اَتَيْنَنِى ثَلَاثَهُنَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arobaEahun~a","text_ar":"اَرْبَعَهُنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but others decline the word with the three vowels, making it like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~uhumo","text_ar":"كُلُّهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": after ten, however, only nasb is used; so that you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atawoniY A^aHada Ea$arahumo","text_ar":"اَتَوْنِى اَحَدَ عَشَرَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapa Ea$arahumo","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةَ عَشَرَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iHodaY Ea$oratahun~a","text_ar":"اـِحْدَى عَشْرَتَهُنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAva","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$oratahun~a","text_ar":"عَشْرَتَهُنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) The saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waladu Alz~inaA $arN Alv~alaAvapi","text_ar":"وَلَدُ الزِّنَا شَرٌ الثَّلَاثَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The offspring of adultery,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fornication, is the worst of the three"},{"kind":"text","text":"] if he do the deeds of his parents. (Mgh.) [It is said that when"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlAvp","text_ar":"ثلاثة"},{"kind":"text","text":"means the things numbered, not the amount of the number, it is imperfectly decl., being regarded as a proper name; and so are other ns. of number. (See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAniypN","text_ar":"ثُمَانِيةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sit~apN","text_ar":"سِتَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapa Ea$ara","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةَ عَشَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[indecl. in every case, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thirteen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is pronounced by some of the Arabs"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapa Eo$ara","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةَ عْشَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and [the fem.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea$orapa","text_ar":"عَشْرَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAva","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", thus in the dial. of El- Hijáz [and of most of the Arabs], is pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAva Ea$irapa","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَ عَشِرَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the dial. of Nejd. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E$r","text_ar":"عشر"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","IAar","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n4630","headword_ar":"ثُلَاثَةٌ","root":"vlv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvapN","text_ar":"ثَلَاثَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}